    <description>Hi there. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Speaking for myself only, I'd like to see auto-attack for ranged weapons added to EverQuest. Clearly the community wants it or it wouldn't be in the ranger's top-10 list. I don't personally see why it should be a big deal to add. But that's just my opinion, which isn't enough to make this happen because this sort of thing requires several key people to agree that it's something we want to do. I have raised the subject on several occasions in the past couple weeks and hopefully the decision making folks will come to a conclusion before too long. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Stuff like this is important to get team discussion and agreement on because it's easy for one person to overlook potential problems (code and/or design) of the side effects of what might otherwise appear to be a simple change, so I don't mind waiting until people come to their own conclusions about it we should do it. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;cheers</description>
