&lt;DIV&gt;For those concerned with it trivalizing events:&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Todays high end ranger with good buffs&amp;nbsp;does ~280dps in melee, ~200dps with a bow on&amp;nbsp;a non moving non rooted target, ~350-400dps for 2min every 67 with trueshot, and about ~80dps on anything soloed with a bow since the mob is rooted or moving.Qvic + level ranger.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Todays high end rogue with good buffs does about ~350-400dps in melee before discs, 500-625dps with melee and discs, ~400-525dps expected 450dps with thrown disc 1 min every 20. Qvic+ level rogue. &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
