&lt;DIV&gt;Heck a necro in 2 spells Prye of Mori + Desecrating Darkness can do 515dmg a tic (85.6dps) before focus items and a 75%snare. Thats already comperable damage&amp;nbsp;to what a ranger can do on a rooted or moving mob and a much better snare (shoter but its got a resist adjust that lets it land without nearly as many casts). Then add in pet and nukes and other dots. Boting a necro would be just as much and probly a lot more dps and utility then boting a ranger. Boting a rogue would be way more damage.&amp;nbsp; Those are not even the "easy" choices like a shaman bot etc.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;If autoarchery does go live please make sure its still easy to fire off just one arrow. Perhapse&amp;nbsp;a /autofire on|off|toggle type command to turn it on, off of flip its state?&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
